   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">The New Program functionality enables you to create programs.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">You can create a program in the following ways:</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">From scratch.</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">From other programs (known as Program Template or Program Accelerator) using the cloning functionality. Any program can function as a program template or accelerator.</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="- topic/p ">To create a program from scratch, you can access the <b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">New Program</b> functionality in the following ways:</p>
